 defenders]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Association football utility players]]\n[[Category:Primeira Liga players]]\n[[Category:Portuguese Second Division players]]\n[[Category:C.D. Nacional players]]\n[[Category:Vit\u00f3ria S.C. players]]\n[[Category:Moreirense F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Portugal youth international footballers]]\n[[Category:Portugal under-21 international footballers]]\n", "name_user": "Quite A Character", "label": "safe", "comment": "Removed overlinking after my new ref additions.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o_Aur%C3%A9lio"}
