us probed in China |date=3 January 2020 |access-date=29 January 2020 |url-status=live |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200105051949/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-50984025 |archive-date=5 January 2020 |work=[[BBC News]]}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"LancetNowcasting\">{{cite journal | vauthors = Perlman S | title = Another Decade, Another Coronavirus | journal = The New England Journal of Medicine | volume = 382 | issue = 8 | pages = 760\u2013762 | date = February 2020 | pmid = 31978944 | pmc = 7121143 | doi = 10.1056/NEJMe2001126 }}</ref>\n<ref name=\"whosituationreports\">{{cite web |url=https://www.who.int/emergencies/diseases/novel-coronavirus-2019/situation-reports |title=Novel Coronavirus 2019 \u2013 Situation Updates |publisher=WHO|access-date= 31 March 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Resnick\">{{cite web |url=https://www.vox.com/science-and-health/2020/3/17/21181694/coronavirus-covid-19-lockdowns-end-how-long-months-years |title=Scientists warn we may need to live with social distancing for a year or more |last=Resnick |first=Brian |date=17 March 2020 |website=Vox |access-date=21 March 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"CDC2020Surfaces\">{{cite web |title=Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19) \u2013 Environmental Cleaning and Disinfection Recommendations |url=https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/prepare/cleaning-disinfection.html |website=Centers for Disease Control and Prevention |access-date=24 March 2020 |date=11 February 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"StableNIH\">{{cite web |title=New coronavirus stable for hours on surfaces |url=https://www.nih.gov/news-events/news-releases/new-coronavirus-stable-hours-surfaces |website=National Institutes of Health (NIH) |access-date=24 March 2020 |date=17 March 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"20200130cdc\">{{cite web |url=https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/summary.html |title=Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19) Situation Summary |date=30 January 2020 |work=US [[Centers for Disease Control and Prevention]] |url-status=liv