r, Xavier}}[[Xavier Dor]]\n|{{age|1929|1|30|2020|04|04}}\n| Embryologist and anti-abortion activist<ref>{{cite web |last1=Pontificum |first1=Summorum |title=Rappel \u00e0 Dieu de Docteur Dor |url=https://www.riposte-catholique.fr/archives/155429 |website=Riposte-catholique |accessdate=5 April 2020 |language=fr-FR |date=4 April 2020}}</ref>\n| France (Paris) \n\n|-\n| {{Date table sorting|2020-04-04|format=md}}\n|{{hs|Farnum, Kenneth}}[[Kenneth Farnum]]\n|{{age|1931|01|18|2020|04|04}}\n| Barbadian-born Jamaican Olympic cyclist<ref>{{cite web |last1=Nye |first1=Peter Joffre |title=Ken Farnum, Olympian and folk hero, dies at age 89 of COVID-19 |url=https://www.cyclingnews.com/news/ken-farnum-olympian-and-folk-hero-dies-at-age-89-of-covid-19/ |website=cyclingnews.com |accessdate=15 April 2020 |language=en}}</ref>\n| United States (New York)\n\n|-\n| {{Date table sorting|2020-04-04|format=md}}\n|{{hs|Islam, Muhammad Sirajul}}[[Muhammad Sirajul Islam]]\n|{{age|1943|01|01|2020|04|04}}\n| Former [[Jatiya Sangsad|member of Bangladeshi parliament]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Ex-Moulvibazar MP Sirajul Islam dies from coronavirus in US |url=https://thefinancialexpress.com.bd/national/ex-moulvibazar-mp-sirajul-islam-dies-from-coronavirus-in-us-1586066210 |website=The Financial Express |accessdate=5 April 2020 |language=en}}</ref>\n| United States (New York)\n\n|-\n| {{Date table sorting|2020-04-04|format=md}}\n|{{hs|Montgomery, Olan}}[[Olan Montgomery]]\n|{{age|1963|4|12|2020|04|04}}\n| Actor and artist<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20200411042243/https://www.dealfuneraldirectors.com/obituary/Timothy-Montgomery \"Timothy Olan Montgomery: April 12, 1963 - April 4, 2020 (Age 56),\"] Deal Funeral Directors, April 10, 2020.</ref>\n| United States (New York) \n\n|-\n| {{Date table sorting|2020-04-04|format=md}}\n|{{hs|Moreau, Marcel}}[[Marcel Moreau]]\n|{{age|1933|4|16|2020|04|04}}\n| Belgian writer<ref>{{cite web |title=D\u00e9c\u00e8s de Marcel Moreau: un \u00e9crivain du d\u00e9bord