ene}}[[Arlene Stringer-Cuevas]]\n|{{age|1933|09|25|2020|04|03}}\n| Former member of the [[New York City Council]]<ref>{{cite web |last1=Calder |first1=Rich |title=Comptroller Scott Stringer\u2019s mom dead from coronavirus |url=https://nypost.com/2020/04/03/comptroller-scott-stringers-mother-arlene-has-died-from-coronavirus/ |website=New York Post |accessdate=5 April 2020 |language=en |date=3 April 2020}}</ref>\n| United States (New York)\n\n|-\n| {{Date table sorting|2020-04-04|format=md}}\n|{{hs|Benedict, Jay}}[[Jay Benedict]]\n|{{age|1951|04|11|2020|04|04}}\n| American actor, who worked mainly in Britain<ref>{{cite web |title=Jay Benedict, \u2018Emmerdale\u2019 and \u2018Aliens\u2019 actor, dies at 68 from COVID-19 |url=https://globalnews.ca/news/6788932/jay-benedict-emmerdale-dead-coronavirus/ |website=Global News |accessdate=8 April 2020 |language=en}}</ref>\n| United Kingdom (London)\n\n|-\n| {{Date table sorting|2020-04-04|format=md}}\n|{{hs|Bodson, Philippe}}[[Philippe Bodson]]\n|{{age|1944|11|2|2020|04|04}}\n| Businessman and politician; former [[Belgian senate|Belgian senator]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Voormalig VBO-voorzitter Philippe Bodson overleden aan coronavirus \n |url=https://www.vrt.be/vrtnws/nl/2020/04/04/bodson-overleden/ |accessdate=4 April 2020 |work=VRT |date=4 April 2020 |language=NL}}</ref>\n| Belgium (Brussels)\n\n|-\n| {{Date table sorting|2020-04-04|format=md}}\n|{{hs|Compton, Forrest}}[[Forrest Compton]]\n|{{age|1925|9|15|2020|04|04}}\n| Actor<ref>{{cite web |title=Update: Town announces the first deaths from coronavirus |url=https://shelterislandreporter.timesreview.com/2020/04/04/town-announces-the-first-deaths-from-coronavirus/ |website=Shelter Island Reporter |accessdate=5 April 2020 |date=4 April 2020}}</ref>\n| United States ([[Shelter Island, New York|Shelter Island]])\n\n|-\n| {{Date table sorting|2020-04-04|format=md}}\n|{{hs|Corral, Florindo}}[[Florindo Corral]]\n|{{age|1949|11|7|2020|04|04}}\n| Businessman<ref>{{cite news |titl